## Routing (React Router v6)
```jsx
import { Link, NavLink, useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom'

// Active link styling
<NavLink
  to="/tasks"
  className={({ isActive }) =>
    isActive ? "bg-gray-700 text-white" : "text-gray-400 hover:text-white"
  }
>
  Tasks
</NavLink>
```

## Environment Variables
```javascript
const BASE_URL = import.meta.env.VITE_API_BASE_URL
// Never hardcode http://localhost:8000
```

## Never
- No class components
- No inline styles
- No external UI libraries (MUI, Chakra, Ant Design)
- No direct fetch() — always use axios via api.js
- No TypeScript — plain JS only
- No prop-types — skip validation for now
